@startuml presence_confirmation_flow
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Segoe UI

[*] --> AwaitingYesNo : comando de presenca reconhecido

AwaitingYesNo --> Cancelled : resposta = NAO
AwaitingYesNo --> Cancelled : 3 tentativas invalidas
AwaitingYesNo --> AwaitingLocationPin : resposta = SIM

AwaitingLocationPin --> Completed : localizacao valida (PIN)
AwaitingLocationPin --> AwaitingLocationPin : localizacao ausente/invalid
AwaitingLocationPin --> Cancelled : timeout da janela de PIN

Completed --> [*]
Cancelled --> [*]

note right of AwaitingYesNo
- Respostas aceites: sim/nao
- 3 tentativas invalidas cancelam
end note

note right of AwaitingLocationPin
- Janela temporal para PIN (LOCATION_PIN_WINDOW_SECONDS)
- PIN obrigatorio para concluir presenca
end note

@enduml
